These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: sprite, milk, cola, iced-tea
Pet: lizard, cat, ferret, guinea-pig
1. Pet:guinea-pig is on the left of Beverage:cola##1
2. Beverage:sprite is on the left of Pet:cat##1
3. Beverage:iced-tea is in an odd position##4
4. Pet:ferret is on the left or right of Pet:guinea-pig##3
5. Beverage:sprite is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | sprite | milk | iced-tea | cola |
| Pet        | lizard | cat   | guinea-pig | ferret    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Movie-Genre: romance, action, drama, sports
Nationality: spanish, indian, colombian, pakistani
1. Movie-Genre:action is on the left of Movie-Genre:sports##1
2. Nationality:spanish is on the left of Nationality:colombian##1
3. Nationality:colombian is in an odd position##4
4. Nationality:spanish == Movie-Genre:romance##1
5. Nationality:indian is on the right of Nationality:colombian##1
6. Nationality:spanish == Movie-Genre:romance##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | romance  | action  | sports |
| Nationality   | pakistani    | spanish | colombian | indian    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Food: kale, pumpkin, peach, cauliflower
Movie-Genre: mystery, action, scientific, time-travel
1. Food:cauliflower is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:time-travel##3
2. Food:peach is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:time-travel is on the left or right of Food:pumpkin##3
4. Movie-Genre:time-travel is on the right of Movie-Genre:scientific##1
5. Movie-Genre:mystery is in an odd position##4
6. Food:pumpkin is on the right of Food:peach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | cauliflower | peach | pumpkin    | kale      |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific        | time-travel     | mystery | action |

