.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
Hobby: card-games, camping, puzzles, board-games
Music-Genre: classical, country, metal, ambient
1. Hobby:camping is between Music-Genre:classical and Music-Genre:ambient##2
2. Hobby:board-games is on the left of Hobby:card-games##1
3. Music-Genre:metal is in an odd position##4
4. Music-Genre:country is on the left of Music-Genre:ambient##1
5. Music-Genre:country is on the right of Hobby:card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | board-games | card-games | camping | puzzles |
| Music-Genre   | metal       | classical   | country    | ambient  |

