.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
Music-Genre: gospel, reggae, pop, soul
Nationality: turkish, japanese, pakistani, egyptian
1. Music-Genre:pop is on the right of Nationality:egyptian##1
2. Nationality:japanese == Music-Genre:soul##1
3. Nationality:pakistani is on the right of Music-Genre:gospel##1
4. Music-Genre:reggae is on the far left##1
5. Music-Genre:pop is in an odd position##4
6. Nationality:turkish is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | reggae  | gospel    | pop   | soul       |
| Nationality   | turkish | egyptian | pakistani | japanese |

