2. Music-Genre:funk is on the right of Beverage:milk##1
3. Music-Genre:rock is between Music-Genre:funk and Beverage:fanta##2
4. Beverage:milk is in an odd position##4
5. Music-Genre:rock is on the left or right of Music-Genre:funk##3
6. Beverage:mirinda is on the left or right of Music-Genre:salsa##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | mirinda       | fanta   | milk | 7up |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | salsa | rock        | funk    |

