.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
Beverage: juice, coffee, tea, mirinda
Food: broccoli, artichoke, mango, eggplant
1. Food:artichoke is on the far left##1
2. Beverage:tea is on the left or right of Beverage:juice##3
3. Beverage:mirinda is on the far left or far right##3
4. Food:mango is on the left of Food:eggplant##1
5. Food:eggplant is on the right of Beverage:juice##1
6. Food:mango is in an even position##4
7. Food:broccoli == Beverage:coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | mirinda | juice    | tea       | coffee |
| Food       | artichoke  | mango | eggplant | broccoli  |

